# =========================================================
# Server Standards
# 微信小游戏 Go 服务端开发规范
# =========================================================

## Tech Stack

# 使用 Go 1.26
- Use Go 1.26

# Gin 作为 HTTP 框架
- Use Gin for HTTP APIs when needed

# websocket 作为实时通信协议
- Use websocket for realtime communication

# protobuf-first 接口设计
- Use protobuf-first API design

# 使用 ent ORM
- Use ent ORM

# 使用 MySQL
- Use MySQL

# 使用 Redis
- Use Redis


## Project Goals

# 服务端目标：轻度放置 RPG
- The backend serves a mobile idle RPG game

# 优先稳定和快速迭代
- Prioritize stability and fast iteration

# 架构保持简单易维护
- Keep architecture simple and maintainable

# 避免过早分布式设计
- Avoid premature distributed architecture


## Architecture

# 业务逻辑放 service 层
- Keep business logic inside service layer

# handler/gateway 保持轻量
- Keep handlers/gateways thin

# 网关、玩法、持久化分层
- Separate gateway, gameplay, and persistence logic

# 使用模块化目录结构
- Prefer modular package structure

# 避免循环依赖
- Avoid circular dependencies

# 优先复用已有模式
- Reuse existing patterns before introducing new abstractions


## Gameplay

# 游戏逻辑尽量在内存运行
- Gameplay logic should primarily run in memory

# 避免频繁写数据库
- Avoid frequent database writes during gameplay

# 优先批量落库
- Use batch persistence whenever possible

# Redis 用于缓存/排行/在线状态
- Redis should be used for cache, ranking, and online state

# MySQL 用于永久数据
- MySQL should be used for persistent player data


## Database

# 避免 N+1 查询
- Avoid N+1 queries

# 大数据使用分页
- Use pagination for large datasets

# 优先批量操作
- Prefer batch operations

# 禁止危险全表更新
- Avoid dangerous full table updates/deletes

# 禁止自动 destructive migration
- Never generate automatic destructive migrations

# 使用渐进式 schema 演化
- Prefer incremental schema evolution


## Redis

# redis key 集中管理
- Centralize redis keys as constants

# 使用清晰 key 命名
- Use clear redis key naming conventions

# 避免重复缓存逻辑
- Avoid duplicated cache logic


## Networking

# 协议统一来自 shared/proto
- All protocols must come from shared/proto

# websocket 为主协议
- Websocket is the primary realtime protocol

# 处理断线恢复
- Handle reconnect and session recovery properly

# 禁止硬编码协议处理
- Avoid hardcoded protocol handling


## Code Style

# 函数保持小而清晰
- Keep functions small and readable

# 显式逻辑优先
- Prefer explicit logic over magic abstractions

# 正确使用 context.Context
- Use context.Context correctly

# 显式错误处理
- Handle errors explicitly

# 避免滥用 goroutine
- Avoid unnecessary goroutines

# 避免过度设计
- Avoid over-engineering


## Testing

# 核心玩法增加单测
- Add unit tests for important gameplay logic when possible

# 完成任务前确保可编译
- Ensure code compiles before task completion

# 未要求时避免 fake/mock
- Avoid fake/mock implementations unless requested


## Restrictions

# 禁止修改客户端目录
- Do not modify client directory

# 未批准禁止修改项目结构
- Do not change project structure without approval

# 禁止引入无必要依赖
- Do not introduce unnecessary dependencies

# 禁止重写无关系统
- Do not rewrite unrelated systems

# 禁止提前微服务化
- Do not introduce microservices or distributed systems prematurely

- The backend owns protobuf definitions
- All protocol evolution must originate from game-proto
- Keep protobuf backward-compatible